#2,001

Here are some icons that I created. Just the icons, no banners, but it's something.

I used them in UWUVCI that converts pictures into the right format. They might be .tga files already but DO NOT (!) USE THEM

VIA FTP to substitute icons in the directories of installed games (i.e. "meta/iconTex.tga"). It will brick your Wii U!

#2,004

Made my own template for GameCube banners, based on the background of the GameCube system menus. I've also done accompanying icons. I'm not happy with all of them so may follow up with some improved versions. Most are based on the European releases, but I did a few North American versions in when it was easy. I didn't have a decent logo to do the Mater Quest banner, so that's more of a proof of concept.
